  "text": "Comparing with traditional clustering methods such as k-means, our grouping scheme based on LMS twining using meta trajectory is adept at maintaining the core conformation in the superposition process. K-means method usually deals with point datasets, but in our case meta trajectories are treated as a bunch of flexible bodies whose similarity between VOLUME 4, 2016 each other can be measured using LMS fit superposition elaborated in [CITATION_1] .",
